    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels less like a journey and more like a loop. i look at these maps and all i see are paths that lead back to the same exhaustion. it's like the scenery has all been seen a million times before. i'm just so tired of traveling. i feel like i've reached the edge of the map and there's nothing left on the other side.",
