      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is entirely okay to step off the road when the journey has lost its meaning, for the only path that truly matters is the one you choose to walk now. You don't need a map to find a new home if you are willing to let go of the old one. Sometimes the bravest thing you can do is simply sit down in the sand and breathe, knowing that you are finally safe.",
      "source": "target",
